OL,3,CTheme park to reopen despite
OL,4,Cliquidation announcement
OL,6,FA popular family-run theme park in
OL,7,FSomerset has announced it will reopen
OL,8,Ffor the 2026 summer season, despite
OL,9,Fappointing liquidators earlier this
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FBrean Theme Park, which first opened
OL,13,Fas a camping and leisure site on Coast
OL,14,FRoad in the village of Brean in the
OL,15,F1940s, has entertained families across
OL,16,Fthe region for decades.
OL,18,FBy 2025, the site had more than 40
OL,19,Frides and opened seasonally from March
OL,20,Fto October.
