OL,3,CTheme park to reopen despite
OL,4,Cliquidation announcement
OL,6,FIn an update, the park's general
OL,7,Fmanager, Peter Mainwaring, said the
OL,8,Fpark will welcome visitors again from
OL,9,FEaster 2026.
OL,11,F"We are working hard behind the scenes
OL,12,Fand will reopen for the 2026 Summer
OL,13,FSeason from Easter," he said.
OL,15,F"Although the group structure has
OL,16,Fchanged, our loyal visitors will still
OL,17,Fenjoy the same park, the same team and
OL,18,Fthe same great day out."
