OL,6,FHe also clarified the park's
OL,7,Frelationship with holiday operator
OL,8,FUnity Holidays.
OL,10,F"Brean Theme Park is not owned by
OL,11,FUnity Holidays," he said. "We operate
OL,12,Fas a fully independent business and
OL,13,Flease land from them. We look forward
OL,14,Fto continuing to work together."
