OL,6,F"We know it has been a challenging
OL,7,Ftime for tourism businesses across the
OL,8,FSouth West. Hinkley Point C is ready
OL,9,Fto support any of the staff facing
OL,10,Fredundancy with the help of our Jobs
OL,11,FService.
OL,13,FThey added: "While most Pontins sites
OL,14,Facross the country have closed, we've
OL,15,Fspent more than #2 million on the
OL,16,FBrean Sands site and have created 80
OL,17,Fyear-round jobs in the community as
OL,18,Fwell as providing funds to support the
OL,19,Fcommunity and local businesses."
